dmca.title: Florida Home Assistant
dmca.body:
My name is Craig Greenfield and I am the owner of the business name Florida Home Assistant.  Please visit the Secretary of State website to confirm at:

http://www.sunbiz.org/scripts/ficidet.exe?action=DETREG&docnum=G05062900103&rdocnum=G05062900103

Please immediately remove all mention of Florida Home Assistant from your website by September 1, 2007.  If you have any questions you can contact me at 678-852-8469.  If you wish to not remove it, then kindly forward your attorney
